00:01:11.490 --> 00:01:12.290 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you.

00:01:12.290 --> 00:01:15.750 align:middle line:84%
>> It's a real pleasure
to be with you.

00:01:15.750 --> 00:01:19.550 align:middle line:84%
