the province of the mind.

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:25.530 align:middle line:90%
Could you begin by--

00:01:25.530 --> 00:01:28.670 align:middle line:84%
>> In the province of mind,
where one believes to be true,

00:01:28.670 --> 00:01:32.960 align:middle line:84%
