true within certain limits.

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:35.570 align:middle line:84%
These limits are to be
found experimentally

00:01:35.570 --> 00:01:37.140 align:middle line:90%
and experientially.

00:01:37.140 --> 00:01:39.860 align:middle line:84%
