were the limits.

00:02:01.580 --> 00:02:04.940 align:middle line:84%
Going into new realities,
taking on the belief systems

00:02:04.940 --> 00:02:07.310 align:middle line:84%
of those realities,
and then coming back

00:02:07.310 --> 00:02:10.490 align:middle line:84%
to your basic working reality
and challenging those beliefs,

00:02:10.490 --> 00:02:13.670 align:middle line:84%
integrating those
beliefs with your own.

00:02:13.670 --> 00:02:17.990 align:middle line:84%
In your writings, you've
explored almost every state

00:02:17.990 --> 00:02:19.550 align:middle line:84%
