levels of Satori,

00:02:21.890 --> 00:02:24.050 align:middle line:84%
communication with
extraterrestrials,

00:02:24.050 --> 00:02:28.190 align:middle line:84%
communication with
other species.

00:02:28.190 --> 00:02:33.800 align:middle line:84%
You've established, probably,
a more significant mapping

00:02:33.800 --> 00:02:39.440 align:middle line:84%
of inner space than almost
any other modern person,

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:44.120 align:middle line:84%
and I think we all owe a
great debt to you for that.

00:02:44.120 --> 00:02:45.370 align:middle line:90%
>> Don't get stuck with those.

00:02:45.370 --> 00:02:46.650 align:middle line:90%
