00:02:53.210 --> 00:02:55.340 align:middle line:84%
>> I think that's the
beauty of your work,

00:02:55.340 --> 00:02:58.750 align:middle line:84%
is that you keep moving
further and further,

00:02:58.750 --> 00:02:59.750 align:middle line:90%
further and further out.

00:02:59.750 --> 00:03:01.370 align:middle line:84%
In The Center of
the Cyclone, you

00:03:01.370 --> 00:03:05.570 align:middle line:84%
described that you had a
whole system, virtually,

00:03:05.570 --> 00:03:07.700 align:middle line:84%
a quantitative
system for mapping

00:03:07.700 --> 00:03:08.870 align:middle line:90%
states of consciousness.

00:03:08.870 --> 00:03:10.970 align:middle line:84%
And you talked about
one that I found

00:03:10.970 --> 00:03:16.310 align:middle line:84%
