describe going so far

00:03:20.750 --> 00:03:23.900 align:middle line:84%
out of your body, even out
of the physical universe,

00:03:23.900 --> 00:03:26.960 align:middle line:84%
to the point of being
at the level of essence

00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:29.860 align:middle line:84%
in which the physical
universe is created.

00:03:29.860 --> 00:03:32.000 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:34.430 align:middle line:84%
>> That almost seemed to me
in reading that book like

00:03:34.430 --> 00:03:36.080 align:middle line:84%
an ultimate state
of consciousness.

00:03:36.080 --> 00:03:39.530 align:middle line:84%
But I know you wrote about
it some 15 years ago.

00:03:39.530 --> 00:03:41.690 align:middle line:90%
How does it look to you now?

00:03:41.690 --> 00:03:44.110 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, there's one
step beyond plus three.

00:03:44.110 --> 00:03:48.770 align:middle line:84%
That's plus one, but you're not
allowed to remember that once

00:03:48.770 --> 00:03:49.790 align:middle line:90%
you go into it.

00:03:49.790 --> 00:03:51.290 align:middle line:90%
You have union with God.

00:03:51.290 --> 00:03:52.220 align:middle line:90%
That's the true yoga.

00:03:52.220 --> 00:03:55.170 align:middle line:90%


00:03:55.170 --> 00:03:56.820 align:middle line:90%
And so you're non-human.

00:03:56.820 --> 00:04:00.010 align:middle line:84%
So there's no way you can
recount what happened.

00:04:00.010 --> 00:04:01.420 align:middle line:90%
You have no way of saying it.

00:04:01.420 --> 00:04:02.900 align:middle line:90%
It goes beyond language.

00:04:02.900 --> 00:04:03.700 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:04:03.700 --> 00:04:06.110 align:middle line:84%
>> All those states
are beyond language.

00:04:06.110 --> 00:04:09.480 align:middle line:84%
Language is a very poor
instrument to express them.

00:04:09.480 --> 00:04:12.480 align:middle line:84%
>> You've described in some of
your other writings language

00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:16.900 align:middle line:84%
as being a film, a thin film
that separates us from reality,

00:04:16.900 --> 00:04:17.700 align:middle line:90%
really.

00:04:17.700 --> 00:04:19.920 align:middle line:84%
As much as we try
to use language

00:04:19.920 --> 00:04:24.400 align:middle line:84%
to describe what we mean,
it really puts barriers up.

00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:28.730 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, there's one use
of language that's valid.

00:04:28.730 --> 00:04:33.261 align:middle line:84%
That's the injunctive use,
telling you how to do things.

00:04:33.261 --> 00:04:37.580 align:middle line:90%
The descriptive one's very poor.

00:04:37.580 --> 00:04:40.052 align:middle line:90%
And William James said it.

00:04:40.052 --> 00:04:42.010 align:middle line:84%
The other realities are
separate from this one,

00:04:42.010 --> 00:04:43.135 align:middle line:90%
but the film is the screen.

00:04:43.135 --> 00:04:46.240 align:middle line:90%


00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:48.928 align:middle line:84%
And I found this
screen is language.

00:04:48.928 --> 00:04:50.470 align:middle line:84%
So you have to
abandon it when you're

00:04:50.470 --> 00:04:53.850 align:middle line:90%
going to these other realities.

00:04:53.850 --> 00:04:56.940 align:middle line:84%
>> In addition to plus
one and plus three,

00:04:56.940 --> 00:04:59.175 align:middle line:90%
you've mapped out plus six.

00:04:59.175 --> 00:05:01.750 align:middle line:90%


00:05:01.750 --> 00:05:04.020 align:middle line:84%
That's a state of
consciousness, as I recall,

00:05:04.020 --> 00:05:07.080 align:middle line:84%
