non-physical space.

00:05:08.820 --> 00:05:11.970 align:middle line:84%
>> But you maintain
your individuality.

00:05:11.970 --> 00:05:16.450 align:middle line:84%
>> That must be a basic
mode of a psychic explorer.

00:05:16.450 --> 00:05:18.990 align:middle line:84%
I gather, from reading
much of your work

00:05:18.990 --> 00:05:22.140 align:middle line:84%
that you've spent a great
deal of time, in plus six.

00:05:22.140 --> 00:05:25.050 align:middle line:90%
>> Right, and in plus 12.

00:05:25.050 --> 00:05:29.160 align:middle line:90%
