now but everything is happy.

00:05:34.520 --> 00:05:37.615 align:middle line:84%
Gold dust particles in the
air, everything is good.

00:05:37.615 --> 00:05:39.990 align:middle line:84%
>> You can feel energy moving
in and out of the different

00:05:39.990 --> 00:05:41.900 align:middle line:90%
