idiot in the same space.

00:05:53.830 --> 00:05:56.590 align:middle line:84%
>> Many of the mystical
teachings warn against getting

00:05:56.590 --> 00:05:58.050 align:middle line:84%
stuck in some of
these realities.

00:05:58.050 --> 00:05:58.850 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:05:58.850 --> 00:06:02.740 align:middle line:84%
I haven't been in any
of them since that time.

00:06:02.740 --> 00:06:06.370 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, you also refer to,
in your mapping of states,

00:06:06.370 --> 00:06:09.830 align:middle line:84%
I suppose, is plus 48, which
is sort of a perfectly neutral

00:06:09.830 --> 00:06:10.630 align:middle line:90%
state.

00:06:10.630 --> 00:06:11.890 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:06:11.890 --> 00:06:16.200 align:middle line:84%
Plus 24 is the professional
state of any discipline

00:06:16.200 --> 00:06:20.527 align:middle line:84%
