00:06:22.110 --> 00:06:23.980 align:middle line:90%
with everybody else.

00:06:23.980 --> 00:06:26.520 align:middle line:84%
And then there are
the minus state,

00:06:26.520 --> 00:06:30.150 align:middle line:90%
