frightened again.

00:07:03.752 --> 00:07:05.850 align:middle line:84%
I was totally
terrified in that one.

00:07:05.850 --> 00:07:08.100 align:middle line:84%
>> I suppose it's what the
Christian mystics sometimes

00:07:08.100 --> 00:07:11.100 align:middle line:84%
referred to as the
dark night of the soul.

00:07:11.100 --> 00:07:14.310 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, it was the
dark night in my soul.

00:07:14.310 --> 00:07:17.700 align:middle line:84%
>> Perhaps this is a necessary
