epitome of terror.

00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:21.240 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:24.720 align:middle line:84%
And for instance, there's
an Iranian psychiatrist

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:26.850 align:middle line:84%
