00:08:11.460 --> 00:08:13.890 align:middle line:84%
Just the way the Iranian
psychiatrist did.

00:08:13.890 --> 00:08:16.360 align:middle line:84%
>> In the realm of the mind
and the province of the mind,

00:08:16.360 --> 00:08:18.840 align:middle line:90%
