00:08:18.840 --> 00:08:22.650 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, you may not be able
to, but you should try it.

00:08:22.650 --> 00:08:24.210 align:middle line:90%
>> I often find in dreams--

00:08:24.210 --> 00:08:26.580 align:middle line:84%
