would destroy the body,

00:08:26.580 --> 00:08:28.290 align:middle line:90%
in the realm of the mind, don't.

00:08:28.290 --> 00:08:30.180 align:middle line:90%
>> That's right.

00:08:30.180 --> 00:08:33.659 align:middle line:84%
The survival programs,
