know what they are so they just

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:32.380 align:middle line:84%
hold the hands of the patient
and help them come out.

00:09:32.380 --> 00:09:35.940 align:middle line:84%
It was the most commonly
used anesthetic in Vietnam.

00:09:35.940 --> 00:09:38.420 align:middle line:90%
Some places won't use it at all.

00:09:38.420 --> 00:09:43.000 align:middle line:84%
>> But basically what a strong
dose of ketamine will do is

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:46.460 align:middle line:90%
