00:09:46.460 --> 00:09:47.310 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, it can.

00:09:47.310 --> 00:09:48.110 align:middle line:90%
>> Mm-hmm.

00:09:48.110 --> 00:09:49.120 align:middle line:90%
>> Mm-hmm.

00:09:49.120 --> 00:09:50.140 align:middle line:90%
